sql.nvtx_kernel_by_pid:
WITH runtime AS (
            SELECT
            r.correlationId AS correlation_id,
            r.start AS r_start,
            r.end AS r_end,
            r.globalTid AS global_tid,
            (CAST(r.globalTid / 16777216 AS INT) % 16777216) AS pid
        FROM CUPTI_ACTIVITY_KIND_RUNTIME r
        WHERE r.correlationId IS NOT NULL AND r.globalTid IS NOT NULL AND r.end IS NOT NULL
          AND (r.globalTid IS NOT NULL)
    ),
    nvtx AS (
        SELECT
            n.start AS n_start,
            n.end AS n_end,
            n.globalTid AS global_tid,
            COALESCE(n.text, s.value) AS range_name
        FROM NVTX_EVENTS n
         LEFT JOIN StringIds s ON s.id = n.textId 
        WHERE n.end IS NOT NULL AND n.end > n.start AND n.eventType IN (59, 60)
          AND n.globalTid IS NOT NULL
    ),
    mapped AS (
        SELECT
            runtime.pid AS pid,
            (k.end - k.start) AS dur_ns,
            (
                SELECT n2.range_name
                FROM nvtx n2
                WHERE n2.global_tid = runtime.global_tid
                  AND n2.n_start <= runtime.r_start
                  AND n2.n_end >= runtime.r_end
                ORDER BY n2.n_start DESC
                LIMIT 1
            ) AS range_name
        FROM CUPTI_ACTIVITY_KIND_KERNEL k
        JOIN runtime ON runtime.correlation_id = k.correlationId
        WHERE k.correlationId IS NOT NULL
          AND k.end IS NOT NULL AND k.end > k.start
          AND runtime.pid IN (?)
        )
        SELECT
        pid,
        range_name,
        COUNT(*) AS kernel_count,
        SUM(dur_ns) AS total_dur_ns,
        AVG(dur_ns) AS avg_dur_ns
    FROM mapped
    WHERE range_name IS NOT NULL
    GROUP BY pid, range_name
    ORDER BY pid, total_dur_ns DESC;

sql.nvtx_kernel_ranges:
WITH runtime AS (
            SELECT
            r.correlationId AS correlation_id,
                r.start AS r_start,
                r.end AS r_end,
            r.globalTid AS global_tid
        FROM CUPTI_ACTIVITY_KIND_RUNTIME r
        WHERE r.correlationId IS NOT NULL AND r.globalTid IS NOT NULL AND r.end IS NOT NULL
        ),
        nvtx AS (
            SELECT
                n.start AS n_start,
                n.end AS n_end,
            n.globalTid AS global_tid,
            COALESCE(n.text, s.value) AS range_name
        FROM NVTX_EVENTS n
         LEFT JOIN StringIds s ON s.id = n.textId 
        WHERE n.end IS NOT NULL AND n.end > n.start AND n.eventType IN (59, 60)
          AND n.globalTid IS NOT NULL
    ),
    mapped AS (
            SELECT
            (k.end - k.start) AS dur_ns,
                (
                SELECT n2.range_name
                    FROM nvtx n2
                    WHERE n2.global_tid = runtime.global_tid
                      AND n2.n_start <= runtime.r_start
                      AND n2.n_end >= runtime.r_end
                    ORDER BY n2.n_start DESC
                    LIMIT 1
            ) AS range_name
        FROM CUPTI_ACTIVITY_KIND_KERNEL k
        JOIN runtime ON runtime.correlation_id = k.correlationId
        WHERE k.correlationId IS NOT NULL
          AND k.end IS NOT NULL AND k.end > k.start
    )
    SELECT
        range_name,
        COUNT(*) AS kernel_count,
        SUM(dur_ns) AS total_dur_ns,
        AVG(dur_ns) AS avg_dur_ns
    FROM mapped
    WHERE range_name IS NOT NULL
    GROUP BY range_name
    ORDER BY total_dur_ns DESC
    LIMIT ?;
